WELCOME!! yes rodcet Nife is the largest guild of family around, (unless the

remember what server they are on either, nor their name :( oh well, one of
them might get these emails and fill us in, until then welcome (you probably
wont see me much, i do have a character on rodcet nife (antony or anthony
sheesh i cant remember which spelling now) but my main character is on
bristlebane Redspider)
